data.description:
Home For Sale in Raymore Missouri
Very well maintained home for sale in the desirable Woods Creek Subdivision in Raymore, Missouri. This 3 bed, 2 ½ bath home has 1,642 finished square feet, a large 2-car garage, sub-basement, large back yard, and newer roof! The updated kitchen with walk-in pantry, vaulted ceilings, and great natural lighting make this home feel very spacious. The master bedroom has 2 walk-in closets as well as full bathroom with separated vanity. Outside, the wide yard has plenty of room for activities and has a small partition to keep dogs enclosed. 
This home is located in southwest Raymore, just a couple of minutes from Interstate 49, giving quick access to surrounding areas. Located in the award winning Raymore-Peculiar school district, kids and families can build their future in this home! The Raymore community is thriving and growing, offering many options for food, shopping, and entertainment. 
Research Belton Hospital is a short drive, just 2.3 miles north. 
2022 Taxes were $2,770.98
